local function StartFires(idFireStart)
	local tFireLocs = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idFireStart, "FireLoc")
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idFireStart, "fxKit_harmless_burst_ignite_fire")
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectDuration(idFireStart, .25)
	for i, idFireLoc in pairs(tFireLocs) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idFireStart) then
			Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroupActorToActor(idFireStart, idFireLoc, ATTRACTOR_FIRE, true)
		end
		Hydra.Wait(0.25)
		Hydra.ActorEnable(idFireLoc)
		Hydra.Wait(0.25)
	end
end

local function FireSpread(idFireStart)
	local tFireLocs = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idFireStart, "FireLoc2")
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idFireStart, "fxKit_harmless_burst_ignite_fire")
	for i, idFireLoc in pairs(tFireLocs) do
		Hydra.ActorEnable(idFireLoc)
		Hydra.Wait(0.5)
	end
end
